<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://student.panmedia.asia/#/index"><img class="alignnone wp-image-190549 size-large" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/06613049735c47ebc8879745b2cd9344-560x207.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="207" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/06613049735c47ebc8879745b2cd9344-560x207.jpg 560w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/06613049735c47ebc8879745b2cd9344-350x129.jpg 350w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/06613049735c47ebc8879745b2cd9344-768x284.jpg 768w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/06613049735c47ebc8879745b2cd9344-30x11.jpg 30w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/06613049735c47ebc8879745b2cd9344.jpg 852w" sizes="(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px"></a></p>
